text: Hermann Baumann (born 23 January 1921) is a retired Swiss freestyle wrestler. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics in London where he won the bronze medal in the freestyle lightweight class. ==References== ==Other websites== *Hermann Baumann at the International Olympic Committee Category:1921 births Category:Possibly living people Category:1948 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Switzerland Category:Swiss wrestlers
